### 注册
POST http://localhost:9080/api/v1/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "test1@test.com"
}

### 登录
POST http://localhost:9080/api/v1/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 测试鉴权（把token换成登录返回的token）
GET http://localhost:9080/api/v1/profile
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoyLCJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InRlc3QiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUxMTQ0ODgsImlhdCI6MTc3NDg1NTI4OH0.m0-QDw-oWYgnu-W3-nmzT1MbFw6atJxtNJJEjMAG80A


### 单轮对话
POST http://localhost:9080/api/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoyLCJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InRlc3QiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUxMTgxNzMsImlhdCI6MTc3NDg1ODk3M30.BXTGG31dltWV1w3xeuw7irgXJVNNRHxZBCP6y8rhxHw

{
  "message": "你好，请介绍一下你自己"
}

### 流式对话
POST http://localhost:9080/api/v1/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoyLCJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InRlc3QiLCJleHAiOjE3NzUxMjA0MDksImlhdCI6MTc3NDg2MTIwOX0.XZXlsJrKdvbo-f8La8m5Mq92LH9eOqHsTNYkiB7yzdw

{
  "message": "请用100字介绍一下Go语言"
}